# Booking — Service endpoints
# UC-012 (create), UC-013 (update, activate, deactivate), list (public)
# TenantContext is populated from X-Tenant-ID / X-Actor-ID headers (set by BFF).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — list services (public — no actor required)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List active services for a tenant (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/services
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — create service (UC-012)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Create a new service (MANAGER role)
POST {{baseUrl}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "Lavagem Completa",
  "description": "Lavagem exterior e interior completa",
  "priceAmount": 150,
  "durationMinutes": 60,
  "loyaltyPointsValue": 10,
  "requiresPickupAddress": false
}

###

### Create a service with pickup address required (STAFF role)
POST {{baseUrl}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: STAFF

{
  "name": "Lavagem Domiciliar",
  "priceAmount": 200,
  "durationMinutes": 90,
  "loyaltyPointsValue": 15,
  "requiresPickupAddress": true
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — update service (UC-013)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Update service name and price (partial update)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "Lavagem Completa Premium",
  "priceAmount": 175
}

###

### Clear description (set to null)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "description": null
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH — activate/deactivate service (UC-013)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Activate a deactivated service
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}/activate
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### Deactivate a service (logical delete — row is preserved)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### 403 — CUSTOMER role not allowed
POST {{baseUrl}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: CUSTOMER
X-Actor-Role: CUSTOMER

{
  "name": "Lavagem Simples",
  "priceAmount": 80,
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "loyaltyPointsValue": 5
}

###

### 400 — Negative price
POST {{baseUrl}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "Lavagem Simples",
  "priceAmount": -50,
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "loyaltyPointsValue": 5
}

###

### 404 — Service not found
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/services/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000099
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "X"
}

###

### 409 — Update on deactivated service
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

{
  "name": "Tentativa apos desativacao"
}
